<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Welcome to ChatBotA4!</h1>
    <hr />
    <h3><b>Allow us to introduce ourselves</b></h3>
    <p>
        We are a group of senior students from the Faculty of Computer Science (Iași, Romania)
        with the sole purpose of giving you a human-like interaction with a ChatBot.
    </p>
    <h3><b>What is our objective?</b></h3>
    <p>
        The project aims to realize an intelligent agent capable to engage meaningful conversations with a
        human user, actively listening and understanding the user, answering questions, discovering the user’s
        personality and suggesting appealing conversation topics. It will emulate a genuine well informed and
        intelligent partner, featuring surprisingly informed answers or bright and funny changes of
        conversation, as well as candid recognition of lack of knowledge.
    </p>
    <h3><b>Our thanks goes to..</b></h3>
    <p>
        Our thanks goes to all the people involved in this project, to our teacher who gave us insight on how to
        manage and split the tasks we had along the way, to each module's team leaders without whom any of this would
        not have been possible and to everybody who gave their time and knowledge for the chatbot.
    </p>
</div>

